<p><font size="4"><b>Seasons</font></b><br>
Retrosheet's goal is to compile game data for every game played throughout major-league history across all of the seasons identified below. For seasons in bold, Retrosheet has compiled play-by-play data for most or all of the major-league games played in those seasons. For seasons in italics, Retrosheet has compiled box-scores for the major-league games played in those seasons. Retrosheet will continue to work on compiling data until all of the seasons below are in bold.
